** Robotics Competition Central Ohio Robotics Initiative (CORI)
------------------------------------------------------------

June 21st

Join hundreds of kids and CORI at this year's CORI Robotics Invitational, held at Dublin Coffman High School. Stop by and checkout the finest robotics teams that Central Ohio has to offer. This will be a great event for student both young and old. Whether your trying to expose a younger student to the amazing field of robotics or you're just looking to have a good time be sure to stop by and check out this worthwhile event.
