** Frog Prince Columbus Children's Theater
------------------------------------------------------------

June 4th - 15th

You can’t judge a book by its cover. Would a prince be princely even if he was green and covered with slime? Would you kiss a frog that was mean, selfish and arrogant – even if you knew he was a prince? Join Columbus Children’s Theatre’s Professional Touring Company as we hop through the hysterical retelling of the Grimm Brothers’ classic tale of humility and forgiveness complete with audience participation.

