------------------------------------------------------------

June 7th

Enjoy CMA Sleuths, a premier tour brought to visitors this summer to celebrate The International Exhibition of Sherlock Holmes on view at COSI. On this tour, you will search for clues to help you investigate and analyze great works of art. This tour is free with museum admission. No reservations are needed.

