** Honey Harvest Stratford Ecological Center
------------------------------------------------------------

June 28th

Join Apiarist Dave Noble for a trip out to the hives to harvest the spring honey crop! You will help open the hives to harvest frames straight from the hive. Then bring the harvest to the 'Honey House' where we will extract the sweet crop from the comb! Plan to stay to enjoy the Honey Bee Festival!

